title: As Time Goes by (1988 - Australia) science fiction comedy
description:
As Time Goes by (1988 - Australia)

Comedy / Science Fiction

starring . . . . Bruno Lawrence, Nique Needles, Ray Barrett
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0094680/


Fantafestival - WON - Best Actor for Bruno Lawrence

Filmed at New South Wales, Australia and Victoria, Australia

This Australian made sci-fi tale is about a surfer who stops in for a bite to eat at a 1940s-type diner. Eventually he realizes that it is not a diner at all, it is a spaceship disguised as one, and the "owners" of the diner are aliens.


Video: XviD, 640x464, 25.000 fps, 900 Kbps, 01h33m55s
Audio: MP3, 48000 Hz, joint stereo, 121 kbps

VHSRip, English audio, no subtitles
